      .brand-subsubtitle Information You Provide to Us
      %p
        We collect information you provide to us, for example when you create or
        modify your account, register to use our Site, purchase services from us,
        request information from us, contact customer support, or otherwise
        communicate with us. This information may include:
      %ul
        %li Name
        %li Address
        %li Billing address
        %li Email address
        %li Telephone number
        %li Employer
        %li Credit card number (solely for payment purposes)
        %li Date of birth
        %li Medical history, medical records and other health related information, including images
        %li Insurance carrier and subscriber information

      - if false
